h2 プリキュアの誕生日

table.table.table-striped.table-hover
  thead
    tr
      th.text-right Date
      th プリキュア名
      th 本名
  tbody
    - @date_girls.each do |date, girl|
      tr class = week_class(date)
        td.text-right = date.strftime("%Y/%m/%d")
        td = girl.precure_name
        td = girl.human_name

